## Alice in Wonderland Fanfiction on Wattpad

### Story Count
While the exact total count isn't provided in the search results, Wattpad hosts Alice in Wonderland stories under multiple tags including "alice-in-wonderland", "aliceinwonderlandfanfiction", and "aliceinwonderland". For comparison, FanFiction.net has over 1,817 Alice in Wonderland stories, suggesting Wattpad likely has a substantial collection as well.

### Popular Tags and Themes
Common tags associated with Alice in Wonderland stories on Wattpad include: aliceinwonderland, wonderland, madhatter, alice, queenofhearts, cheshirecat, whiterabbit, fantasy, disney, redqueen, adventure, hatter, whitequeen, cheshire, fanfiction, peterpan, fairytale, magic, descendants, and mad.

### Popular Story Types
The fanfiction includes various popular themes:
- Crossovers with other fandoms like Twilight
- Disney Descendants-related stories featuring characters from Wonderland
- Once Upon a Time crossovers
- Mad Hatter x Alice romance stories
- Stories set in Wonderland as part of the Isle of the Lost universe

### Trending Elements
Popular fanfiction trends include:
- Modern retellings and contemporary settings
- Romance-focused narratives, particularly featuring the Mad Hatter
- Next-generation stories featuring descendants of original characters
- Crossovers with other Disney properties and fairy tales
- Dark or twisted versions of the classic tale

The Alice in Wonderland fandom remains very active on Wattpad, with stories spanning multiple sub-genres and attracting readers interested in both classic retellings and innovative crossovers.
